                    <p style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                        I am a Yoga Alliance certified Yoga Teacher with more than 10 years of experience teaching in various studios. Offering well-being by means of holistic tools such as yoga, meditation and mindfulness is my passion.  .
                    </p>
